| ðŸ§  Security Architecture       | Complex hybrid environments need secure-by-design systems                              | CISSP, SABSA, TOGAF, cloud architecture                                   |
| â˜ï¸ Cloud Security              | Migration to AWS, Azure, GCP with misconfiguration risks                               | CCSP, AWS Security, Azure SC-900, Kubernetes, Terraform                   |
| ðŸ§¬ Identity & Access Management (IAM) | Zero Trust adoption, insider threat mitigation                                       | Azure AD, Okta, SailPoint, IAM governance frameworks                      |
| ðŸ§¯ Incident Response & Forensics | SOC maturity, ransomware recovery, legal evidence handling                            | GCIH, CHFI, DFIR, Splunk, Wireshark, chain-of-custody protocols           |
| ðŸ” Application Security        | DevSecOps integration, secure coding, API protection                                   | OWASP, CSSLP, SAST/DAST tools, SDLC governance                           |
| ðŸ›°ï¸ OT & ICS Security           | Industrial systems (energy, water, manufacturing) increasingly targeted                | GRID, ISA/IEC 62443, SCADA protocols, physicalâ€“digital risk mapping       |
| ðŸ§­ Cybersecurity Strategy & Policy | Boardroom alignment, national frameworks, Responsible AI integration                  | CISSP, CISM, policy drafting, stakeholder engagement                      |
| ðŸ§‘â€âš–ï¸ Legal & Regulatory Tech   | POPIA, GDPR, AI Act, cross-border data governance                                     | LegalTech, data protection law, compliance automation                     |
| ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ« Security Awareness & Training | Human error remains top breach vectorâ€”culture change is critical                      | Train-the-trainer, phishing simulation tools, behavioural psychology      |
| ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ’» Bug Bounty & Freelance Security | Crowdsourced testing, agile vulnerability discovery                                  | HackerOne, Bugcrowd, VDP frameworks, ethical hacking credentials          |

